[The Miss World 2017](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miss_World_2017) beauty
pageant will take place in November 2017 in China. [Jessia
Islam](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jessia_Islam) will represent Bangladesh.

